{"tid":1057983,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇狗(蘇拿利)都躝撚左 幾時到蘇狗(蘇斯克查)?","createTime":"2019-03-12T08:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T12:47:57.000Z","uid":12034,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8b31fcde484f36fa41797e592553b7c95a9b2087","tid":1057983,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:37:10.000Z","msg":"佢其實老屎忽同做傀儡，仲有咩條件令佢成為頂級領隊？<br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n2. <br />\n3. <br />\n4. <br />\n<br />\n其實佢只係廢老一個，只不過係懶有歷史嘅廢老。<br />\n睇到悶啦，不如佢都係躝啦屌！<br />\n<br />\n撐左曼聯咁耐，真係比人話垃圾都無咁嬲。 睇住一手好牌，比班垃圾阿狗禁住打，真係灰到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n蘇狗，屌你老母！躝啦！還我曼雲高爾！"},{"pid":"a4da328a63695ea44f6964718bfca95b2aecc0f2","tid":1057983,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"蘇斯查克真係狗來"},{"pid":"62d4e8759b513f219a4dfda7d13c1ea5f6420041","tid":1057983,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:45:45.000Z","msg":"睇完一集何蛇分析蘇b先再出post喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ef15c5bf6ae0fe5527ce99b07afaca8fb0aab8","tid":1057983,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4da328a63695ea44f6964718bfca95b2aecc0f2","tid":1057983,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"蘇斯查克真係狗來"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"就快用晒D查克拉"},{"pid":"05f2c8e87840f1e61925f28a32245fa8cc4655cc","tid":1057983,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62d4e8759b513f219a4dfda7d13c1ea5f6420041","tid":1057983,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:45:45.000Z","msg":"睇完一集何蛇分析蘇b先再出post喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:19:34.000Z","msg":"我中三程度 何sir真太高深睇唔明"},{"pid":"f13f19b245537c5e2c00d35ac6345156cab2fcae","tid":1057983,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05f2c8e87840f1e61925f28a32245fa8cc4655cc","